Message.SourceString: I'm looking for an undead ranger's bow. Perhaps it's another weapon in one of those dragonkin vaults?
Message.LocalizedString: I'm looking for an undead ranger's bow. Perhaps it's another weapon in one of those dragonkin vaults?

Message.SourceString: It may not sound like much, but sharing knowledge is what turns a gathering of people into a thriving community.
Message.LocalizedString: It may not sound like much, but sharing knowledge is what turns a gathering of people into a thriving community.

Message.SourceString: We're looking for a shadow sword. When I was investigating the area the clues I found pointed to one of those zogre things. You might need to kill quite a few of them.
Message.LocalizedString: We're looking for a shadow sword. When I was investigating the area the clues I found pointed to one of those zogre things. You might need to kill quite a few of them.

Message.SourceString: You know what, we make a good team, you and I. You find me things and I record them for future crafters to enjoy.
Message.LocalizedString: You know what, we make a good team, you and I. You find me things and I record them for future crafters to enjoy.

Message.SourceString: So, what do you say to helping me out a bit more?
Message.LocalizedString: So, what do you say to helping me out a bit more?

Message.SourceString: Sounds familiar, doesn't it? A land full of the undead, with deadly monsters roaming around. I'm now wondering if the story came from here somehow.
Message.LocalizedString: Sounds familiar, doesn't it? A land full of the undead, with deadly monsters roaming around. I'm now wondering if the story came from here somehow.

Message.SourceString: Thanks for all your help. Ashenfall really is home to some remarkable weapons. I wonder what else we'll uncover? My boy, Boric, would love this place.
Message.LocalizedString: Thanks for all your help. Ashenfall really is home to some remarkable weapons. I wonder what else we'll uncover? My boy, Boric, would love this place.

Message.SourceString: I've got a little something to thank you for your efforts so far, but you seem a bit overburdened. I'll hold on to it til you've got your hands a bit freer.
Message.LocalizedString: I've got a little something to thank you for your efforts so far, but you seem a bit overburdened. I'll hold on to it til you've got your hands a bit freer.

Message.SourceString: That's it! That's the bow! It looks just like the story described. I wonder...

Message.SourceString: Here, my little way of saying thank you.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, my little way of saying thank you.

Message.SourceString: Well now, there you have it! A shadow sword!
Message.LocalizedString: Well now, there you have it! A shadow sword!

Message.SourceString: Wonderful. Now then, I once told me lad about this strange warrior from far away. Fought great evil, undead beasties and the like.
Message.LocalizedString: Wonderful. Now then, I once told me lad about this strange warrior from far away. Fought great evil, undead beasties and the like.

Message.SourceString: Ah, yes, you must be quite busy. Well, I won't keep you. If you're bored later, come say hi.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah, yes, you must be quite busy. Well, I won't keep you. If you're bored later, come say hi.

Message.SourceString: As the tale goes, the warrior first had to face off against a deadly archer. All bone and dark magic. Had this skeletal bow that was described in eerie detail.
Message.LocalizedString: As the tale goes, the warrior first had to face off against a deadly archer. All bone and dark magic. Had this skeletal bow that was described in eerie detail.

Message.SourceString: Oh, yes, like that one you have there!

Message.SourceString: If it's anything like the bow, it'll be stored in a vault somewhere. Can you bring it to me? It'll really help with my research.
Message.LocalizedString: If it's anything like the bow, it'll be stored in a vault somewhere. Can you bring it to me? It'll really help with my research.

Message.SourceString: Alright, last piece of the puzzle. There's this special sword that I need. Made of shadow, or smoke or something. Nasty thing, wielded by something proper wicked.
Message.LocalizedString: Alright, last piece of the puzzle. There's this special sword that I need. Made of shadow, or smoke or something. Nasty thing, wielded by something proper wicked.

Message.SourceString: The good news, is that I'm pretty sure it's not in a vault. The bad news is that I'm pretty sure it's in the possession of one of them enormous zogre thingies. You might need to kill quite a few of them to find it.
Message.LocalizedString: The good news, is that I'm pretty sure it's not in a vault. The bad news is that I'm pretty sure it's in the possession of one of them enormous zogre thingies. You might need to kill quite a few of them to find it.

Message.SourceString: It's all like the story. You know, I used to tell my boy this story, good old Boric. He was so excited to hear the tale of heroic warriors and undead monsters.
Message.LocalizedString: It's all like the story. You know, I used to tell my boy this story, good old Boric. He was so excited to hear the tale of heroic warriors and undead monsters.

Message.SourceString: To think, I'm standing in the very land this story took place. Boric would love to hear this... if... if I ever get a chance to see him again of course.
Message.LocalizedString: To think, I'm standing in the very land this story took place. Boric would love to hear this... if... if I ever get a chance to see him again of course.

Message.SourceString: Ah don't mind me. Just a melancholic old man worried about his fully grown and perfectly capable boy. I just don't tell him enough how proud of him I am.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah don't mind me. Just a melancholic old man worried about his fully grown and perfectly capable boy. I just don't tell him enough how proud of him I am.

Message.SourceString: Anyway, here, have this. My little way of saying thank you for helping an old codger like me connect to happy memories.
Message.LocalizedString: Anyway, here, have this. My little way of saying thank you for helping an old codger like me connect to happy memories.

Message.SourceString: OK, let's look at the next part of the story. There was a necromancer, nasty piece of work, with a powerful magic staff.
Message.LocalizedString: OK, let's look at the next part of the story. There was a necromancer, nasty piece of work, with a powerful magic staff.

Message.SourceString: I... I'm just gonna sit here with me memories for a bit. You go on now, don't let an old git like me sour your mood. Thank you again, friend.
Message.LocalizedString: I... I'm just gonna sit here with me memories for a bit. You go on now, don't let an old git like me sour your mood. Thank you again, friend.
